data.description: Meet the new "crib" on the block! This charming semi detached home in Baltimore is waiting for its new owner. Fully renovated 6 years ago... this meticulously maintained,  this home offers 3 well sized bedrooms & 2 updated baths. Open concept main level flows into the kitchen & has stainless steel appliances. The large deck off of the kitchen sits above a large backyard. The finished basement is icing on the cake! Nearby elementary/ middle school is within short walking distance.  *Sold as is but will pass city grant incentive Inspections * *$2000 credit given for cosmetics* First Buyer's financing fell thru before. Inspection is complete & available for next buyer.
